cluster Image f -> commutative;
coherence
 proof
 set I = Image f;
 let u,v be Element of I;
 consider a being Element of R such that A1: f.a = u by T6;
 consider b being Element of R such that A2: f.b = v by T6;
 thus u * v = f.b * f.a by A1,A2,T5
   .= v * u by A1,A2,T5;
